The use of probabilistic analysis and algorithms also suggests a connection to algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). The mention of networks and communication cost points towards network architecture and protocols (cs.NE). The use of dynamic load balancing and local schemes suggests a connection to control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the use of algorithms and probabilistic analysis also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
